net.sourceforge.waters.model.module

Interface ComponentProxy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<NamedProxy>, ComparableProxy<NamedProxy>, IdentifiedProxy, NamedProxy, Proxy
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    InstanceProxy, SimpleComponentProxy, VariableComponentProxy
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComponentElement, InstanceElement, SimpleComponentElement, VariableComponentElement

    public interface ComponentProxy
extends IdentifiedProxy
    The common interface for all components in a Waters module. This interface represents the proper items that may occur in a module's component list. Presently, these are simple components (SimpleComponentProxy), variables (VariableComponentProxy), and instances (InstanceProxy).
    Author:
    Robi Malik
    See Also:
    SimpleComponentProxy, VariableComponentProxy, InstanceProxy
